metadata.name: I ain’t gonna stop..
metadata.description:
Never give up on something that you can’t go a day without thinking about and that thing for me is “Art”. I will never stop painting no matter what.
Don’t let anything stop you. There will be times when you’ll be disappointed, but you can’t stop. Keep doing your thing your hard work will pay off one day.

Resolution:- 3000×4000
Dpi:- 300
Software:- Procreate
